{"tid":1506571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場派同街頭派請進","createTime":"2019-08-26T00:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:43:19.000Z","uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f3de061db512f5d01364f9b5bea3dc4e644e6994","tid":1506571,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:16:58.000Z","msg":"我支持91入機，什至9月頭兩個禮拜全入機場<br />\n<br />\n但假設政府仲係拖全無反應<br />\n<br />\n要把握時間10.1前再上街遊行<br />\n<br />\n因為而家支共重點係止暴，如果10.1真係停曬所有遊行，只會俾政府落重藥以為成功止暴開心過國慶<br />\n<br />\n我唔係鼓勵送頭，但可以盡可能解決無黨鐵去游擊，仲有時間諗諗<br />\n<br />\n記住要點，無五大訴求，機場同街頭兩樣都唔可以停！"},{"pid":"8a7a729758f704bdc3309d2ee2b113dbda18d630","tid":1506571,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:28:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"90d2aeca130053f352b384c7c3a306027fac5898","tid":1506571,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxm9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=05a8bbe5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n英文文宣建議：<br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f27f56fc880223bc59c9704ae025cc49a8ed4014","tid":1506571,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"}]}